org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model

Interface TextComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, ReadableComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TextComponentImpl

    public interface TextComponent
extends ReadableComponent
    A representation of the model object 'Text Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Descriptor
    • Width
    • Height
    • Date
    • Text Height
    • Text Map

    See Also:
    DetailViewPackage.getTextComponent()
